00:03:32.780 --> 00:03:37.340
And many people would
regard it as one

00:03:37.340 --> 00:03:38.870
of the funniest
books ever written

00:03:38.870 --> 00:03:39.960
in the English language.

00:03:39.960 --> 00:03:42.060
I'm among them.

00:03:42.060 --> 00:03:44.900
And this is Bierce.

00:03:44.900 --> 00:03:47.490
