the importance of combining

00:52:46.370 --> 00:52:51.080
patience with what Charlie
Munger likes to call gumption--

00:52:51.080 --> 00:52:56.530
you know, extreme determination
at the right moment.

00:52:56.530 --> 00:53:00.680
And if you have the
sort of temperament

00:53:00.680 --> 00:53:04.610
where, in a period like
the fourth quarter of 2008

00:53:04.610 --> 00:53:08.680
