that maybe the investors didn't

00:59:08.230 --> 00:59:11.070
apply to dig deeper?

00:59:11.070 --> 00:59:12.530
JASON ZWEIG: Yeah.

00:59:12.530 --> 00:59:19.320
I think the recent collapse
